{"word":"H8176 - שָׁעַר - shâʻar - shaw-ar' - Think - யோசி","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>שָׁעַר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâʻar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-ar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Think / யோசி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நினைவு, பிள, பிரி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to split open, to reason out, to calculate, to reckon, to estimate"},{"paragraph":"(Qal) to calculate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>split</i> or <i>open</i>, that is, (literally, but only as denominative from <a href=\"#/H8179 - שַׁעַר - shaʻar - shah'-ar/8179\">H8179</a>) to <i>act as gate keeper</i> (see <a href=\"#/H7778 - שֹׁועֵר - shôwʻêr - sho-are'/7778\">H7778</a>); (figuratively) to <i>estimate: - </i>think."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8176 - שָׁעַר - shâʻar - shaw-ar'/8176\">H8176</a>, <a href=\"#/H8180 - שַׁעַר - shaʻar - shah'-ar/8180\">H8180</a>"}]}